text:
Can you just set cookies with same name that HubSpot uses? For example enable tracking:

```document.cookie = "__hs_opt_out=no; expires=Thu, 18 Dec 2023 12:00:00 UTC; path=/";
document.cookie = "__hs_initial_opt_in=yes; expires=Thu, 18 Dec 2023 12:00:00 UTC; path=/";

// Remove "do not track" by setting cookie date last year
document.cookie = "__hs_do_not_track; expires=Thu, 18 Dec 2020 12:00:00 UTC; path=/";```
